OL,6,FMore than 100 people have been
OL,7,Farrested for domestic abuse offences
OL,8,Fin Gloucestershire so far this
OL,9,FDecember, 2024.
OL,11,FPolice revealed that in the first 15
OL,12,Fdays of December, 113 people have been
OL,13,Farrested for offences related to
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse.
OL,16,FMore than 85% of those arrested were
OL,17,Fmen and more than half were in
OL,18,Fconnection with a physical assault on
OL,19,Fa partner, former partner or family
OL,20,Fmember.
